                      Brainex Registration Agreement
                      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
      
 Registration of Brainex Doors entitles you to unlimited FREE future 
 upgrades. Free upgrades will be in the form of ZIP files, which may 
 be downloaded from The Brainex System Web Page at: www.brainex.com.
 If you wish to receive upgrades by mail, there will be a charge of $5.00
 per upgrade  sent to cover the cost of the disk and shipping. 

 To obtain a REGISTRATION NUMBER for a Brainex Door, please fill 
 out the order form below, sign it, then mail it, along with a check,
 money order, or credit card number to the address below.  You will be
 mailed the registration number.

 To order online by Credit Card, visit www.brainex.com. Internet orders
 are  processed withn 24 hours and your registration number will be sent
 via Internet email unless otherwise indicated.

 If you wish to have your Registration number posted to you on
 your BBS, FAX, or if you wish to be called by voice, please include an 
 extra $5.00, and you will be called you as soon as your order is 
 processed! If you are local to Los Angeles, you will be called at
 no charge. For faster service by mail, please use a MONEY ORDER. All
 checks must clear the bank before any numbers are sent to you.

 Brainex Doors are released "As Is" and there is *NO* warranty or 
 guarantee that they will work for you and not cause any problems. 
 PLEASE BE SURE THE BRAINEX PROGRAMS WORK TO YOUR SATISFACTION BEFORE 
 PLACING YOUR ORDER. Stanley Sheff (author) will not be held responsible 
 for any problems you may have, whether directly or indirectly due to the 
 use of any Brainex Program or its utilities or associated 
 files.

 Prices as of 01/01/96.  All Prices subject to change.  By signing and
